#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.nansum.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.nansum"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nansum.nansum:1 of
msgid ""
"Return the sum of array elements over a given axis treating Not a Numbers"
" (NaNs) as zero."
msgstr "返回给定轴上数组元素的总和，并将非数字（NaN）视为零。"

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nansum.nansum:4 of
msgid "Zero is returned for slices that are all-NaN or empty."
msgstr "对于全为 NaN 或空的切片，返回零。"

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nansum.nansum of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nansum.nansum:7 of
msgid ""
"Tensor containing numbers whose sum is desired. If `a` is not an tensor, "
"a conversion is attempted."
msgstr "包含所需总和数字的张量。如果 `a` 不是张量，则会尝试转换。"

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nansum.nansum:10 of
msgid ""
"Axis along which the sum is computed. The default is to compute the sum "
"of the flattened array."
msgstr "计算总和的轴。默认计算展平数组的总和。"

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nansum.nansum:13 of
msgid ""
"The type of the returned tensor and of the accumulator in which the "
"elements are summed.  By default, the dtype of `a` is used.  An exception"
" is when `a` has an integer type with less precision than the platform "
"(u)intp. In that case, the default will be either (u)int32 or (u)int64 "
"depending on whether the platform is 32 or 64 bits. For inexact inputs, "
"dtype must be inexact."
msgstr ""
"返回张量的类型以及元素相加时累加器的类型。默认使用 `a` 的 dtype。一个例外"
"是当 `a` 具有比平台 (u)intp 更低精度的整数类型时。在这种情况下，默认值将"
"是 (u)int32 或 (u)int64，具体取决于平台是 32 位还是 64 位。对于非精确输入"
"，dtype 必须是非精确的。"

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nansum.nansum:20 of
msgid ""
"Alternate output tensor in which to place the result.  The default is "
"``None``. If provided, it must have the same shape as the expected "
"output, but the type will be cast if necessary.  See `doc.ufuncs` for "
"details. The casting of NaN to integer can yield unexpected results."
msgstr ""
"用于放置结果的替代输出张量。默认为 ``None``。如果提供，它必须与预期输出"
"具有相同形状，但如有必要，类型将被转换。有关详细信息，请参见 `doc.ufuncs`"
"。将 NaN 转换为整数可能会产生意外结果。"

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nansum.nansum:26 of
msgid ""
"If this is set to True, the axes which are reduced are left in the result"
" as dimensions with size one. With this option, the result will broadcast"
" correctly against the original `a`."
msgstr ""
"如果设置为 True，则被规约的轴在结果中保留为大小为一的维度。使用此选项，"
"结果将能正确地与原始 `a` 进行广播。"

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nansum.nansum of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nansum.nansum:36 of
msgid ""
"**nansum** -- A new tensor holding the result is returned unless `out` is"
" specified, in which it is returned. The result has the same size as `a`,"
" and the same shape as `a` if `axis` is not None or `a` is a 1-d array."
msgstr ""
"**nansum** -- 除非指定了 `out`，否则将返回一个包含结果的新张量。结果的"
"大小与 `a` 相同，如果 `axis` 不为 None 或 `a` 是一维数组，则形状也相同。"

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nansum.nansum of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nansum.nansum:44 of
msgid ":py:obj:`mt.sum`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nansum.nansum:45 of
msgid "Sum across tensor propagating NaNs."
msgstr "对张量进行求和并传播 NaN。"

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nansum.nansum:47 of
msgid ":py:obj:`isnan`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nansum.nansum:48 of
msgid "Show which elements are NaN."
msgstr "显示哪些元素是 NaN。"

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nansum.nansum:50 of
msgid ":py:obj:`isfinite`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nansum.nansum:51 of
msgid "Show which elements are not NaN or +/-inf."
msgstr "显示哪些元素不是 NaN 或 +/-inf。"

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nansum.nansum:54 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nansum.nansum:55 of
msgid ""
"If both positive and negative infinity are present, the sum will be Not A"
" Number (NaN)."
msgstr "如果同时存在正无穷和负无穷，总和将是非数字（NaN）。"

